data.description: This townhouse boasts an inviting Southwestern facade, with earthy stucco & adobe accents, complemented by a reflective flat roof. At the heart of this residence is the enclosed courtyard, a tranquil oasis that provides privacy & an ideal outdoor living space. The kitchen is a culinary haven, complete with a center island that provides both additional counter space and storage. The kitchen has a cozy breakfast nook area, illuminated by natural light filtering through a large window. The living room centers around a beehive fireplace, making it a perfect spot to gather around during chilly desert evenings. The Arizona room, adjacent to the living area, is a flexible space that can serve as an office or den. Furnishings are available as a separate bill of sale. Enjoy access to Green Valley Recreation (GVR) amenities. Whether it's access to pools, fitness centers, or community events, GVR provides a wide range of activities for active living. In conclusion, this townhouse is a harmonious blend of Southwestern charm, modern comfort, and versatility. It embraces the beauty of the Arizona desert while providing all the comforts of home.
